{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/go-bdd/gobdd/releases/23363563", "assets_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/go-bdd/gobdd/releases/23363563/assets", "upload_url": "https://uploads.github.com/repos/go-bdd/gobdd/releases/23363563/assets{?name,label}", "html_url": "https://github.com/go-bdd/gobdd/releases/tag/v0.6.0", "id": 23363563, "author": {"login": "bkielbasa", "id": 1235620, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEyMzU2MjA=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1235620?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bkielbasa", "html_url": "https://github.com/bkielbasa", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bkielbasa/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bkielbasa/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bkielbasa/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bkielbasa/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bkielbasa/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bkielbasa/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bkielbasa/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bkielbasa/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bkielbasa/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "node_id": "MDc6UmVsZWFzZTIzMzYzNTYz", "tag_name": "v0.6.0", "target_commitish": "master", "name": "Simplified AddStep function", "draft": false, "prerelease": false, "created_at": "2020-02-03T16:52:46Z", "published_at": "2020-02-04T07:25:26Z", "assets": [], "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/go-bdd/gobdd/tarball/v0.6.0", "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/go-bdd/gobdd/zipball/v0.6.0", "body": "1. Right now, `AddStep` doesn't return errors. Errors are logged in `Run()` function instead.\r\n\r\nBefore:\r\n```go\r\nerr := suite.AddStep(\"\", someFunc) // err contains an error\r\nif err != nil {\r\n    t.Fatal(err)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nafter:\r\n```go\r\nsuite.AddStep()\r\n